From: Chris Wilson <chris@chris-wilson.co.uk>
Date: Thu, 22 Feb 2018 09:25:45 +0000
Subject: drm/i915/breadcrumbs: Assert all missed breadcrumbs were signaled
Git-commit: 9792e213a4c9b16b814c0865ea0cc5d5125e052b
Patch-mainline: v4.17-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

When parking the engines and their breadcrumbs, if we have waiters left
then they missed their wakeup. Verify that each waiter's seqno did
complete.

Signed-off-by: Chris Wilson <chris@chris-wilson.co.uk>
